room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Challenge" by Quest Room in Los Angeles
room_address: 170 South Western Avenue, Los Angeles, CA 90004
room_description: You live in Italy in the year 1493. The name of the Master Leonardo Da Vinci is known all around the world. Hundreds of students start to follow him, hoping that grand inventor will take them under his wing as an apprentice. There are so many young hopefuls, that Da Vinci built a room specifically designed to select candidates. Only the students capable of exiting this room in one hour will be granted the honor to learn from Master Leonardo!
